item.description: 🍵 October 22, 2024 “We all start as strangers, but we forget that we rarely choose who ends up a stranger too.” — Brianna Wiest, How The People We Once Loved Become Strangers Again 🍵 April 24, 2023 “Beware of he who would deny you access to information, for in his heart he dreams himself your master” — Pravin Lal, Sid Meier’s Alpha Centauri 🍵 June 4, 2021 “The Answer to the Great Question… Of Life, the Universe and Everything… Is… Forty-two.

item.title: About
item.description: Hi, my name is Quý (he/him). I’m currently working as a Backend engineer at Zalo Group. I studied Computer Science at the Ho Chi Minh City University of Technology. I have a thirst for knowledge and learning new things. This is my personal blog, content is primarily focused on, but not limited to programming. Personal I love making new friends with people around the world 📬. Feel free to drop me a message if you want to know more about me.
